<html>
  <%- include('./include/head'); -%>
  <body>

  <%if(isAdmin){%>
    <%- include('./include/navbarAdmin'); -%>
  <%}
  else{%>
    <%- include('./include/navbar'); -%>
  <%}%>
  <%if(signedup){%>
    <h3 class="text-success text-center">Your account has been created</h3>
  <%}%>
  <main id="accueil" class="border rounded-0 border-dark shadow-lg mx-auto mt50">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col">
            <article class="color-white">
              <h1 class="w-100 text-center">Welcome on the first PolyEsports Website</h1>
              <p>
                <br>
                <br>
              </p>
              <p>Here is a little introduction to show you how to use the web site.</p>
              <br>

              <p>Let's begin with the basics. After creating your account and verifying it, you will be able to access to your <strong>Profile&nbsp;</strong>section. In this section you will be able to change the information you provided including your password. You will also have the possibilty to c<strong>reate your team</strong> !
                <br>
                <br>
              </p>
              <p>About the teams, all teams are displayed in the "<strong>Teams</strong>" Section. Anyone can see everyone's team and <strong>request to join it</strong>. Only the captain of the team can accept these requests. If you want to send a request to another team, you will have to cancel the first request. In the case where you are the only member of your team and you want to <strong>dismantle </strong>it, you will just have to remove yourself.&nbsp;</p>
              <p>
                <br>
              </p>
              <p>Let's talk about the <strong>Tournament </strong>section now ! You will be able to see every open tournaments and have more information about by clicking on the button to see more. To join a tournament, the captain of your team will be the only member allowed to sign your team and leave it.&nbsp;</p>
              <p>During the tournament Matches will be added and the rest is in your hands !&nbsp;</p>
              <p>
                <br>
              </p>
              <p>Enjoy !&nbsp;</p>

            </article>
